metadata.name: cLoUd DuDe #1
metadata.description: Cloud Dudes don't know what sadness. Clouds are positive. Be like the Clouds! :) Cloud Dudes NFT Community is the collection of 9999 NFTs that was generated on the Ethereum blockchain!  Each Cloud is unique! The Clouds are so light and free. Therefore, each Cloud symbolizes the freedom of life and choice. Life is a beautiful thing not to be missed! And Cloud Dudes are good at it! When you look at the Clouds, know that they will also look at you :) Let's go to the Cloud World! Cloud-Butler will help you! Follow him!
